{"title":"路","authors":["牛其峰"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛其峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么，让我躺倒为路吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉车轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝固的目光竖起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为可靠的路标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，躺倒决不就是遗憾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条河不是已被我的身躯劈断了吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果有涛声轰然而至"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一定是颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叙说某个时刻的悲壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以最勇敢的姿势倒下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将青春的生命昭示天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸展一个顽强的意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起手臂　像旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤旅人在我的胸膛之上大步前行"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}